casebody.data:
GERARD
v.
ORANGE COAST MEMORIAL MEDICAL CENTER S225205 Supreme Court of California August 17, 2016 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-captioned matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Appellate District, Division Three, with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the cause in light of the enactment of Statutes 2015, chapter 505 (Sen. Bill No. 327 (2015-2016 Reg. Sess.)). (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
